rowing%20group%20of%20Southeast%20Asian%20startups%20building%20products%20for%20US-based%20customers%2C%20rather%20than%20those%20in%20their%20backyard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20these%20software%20startups%2C%20the%20US's%20rising%20isolationism%20isn't%20threatening%20their%20customer%20base%20%E2%80%94%20yet.%20But%20sweeping%20tariffs%20on%20China%20may%20push%20up%20the%20cost%20of%20hardware%20they%20need%20to%20import%20into%20the%20US%2C%20such%20as%20servers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTraditionally%2C%20Southeast%20Asian%20startups%20honed%20in%20on%20local%20or%20regional%20markets%20to%20solve%20unique%2C%20homegrown%20challenges%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jussi%20Salovaara%2C%20a%20cofounder%20of%20Antler%20who%20leads%20investments%20in%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ride-hailing%20apps%20Grab%20and%20GoJek%20%E2%80%94%20two%20of%20the%20region's%20best-known%20startups%2C%20now%20publicly%20listed%20%E2%80%94%20are%20examples%20of%20how%20founders%20in%20the%20early%202010s%20built%20for%20local%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20as%20the%20ecosystem%20matures%2C%20founders%20are%20now%20setting%20their%20sights%20on%20the%20US%2C%20encouraged%20by%20a%20blend%20of%20opportunity%20and%20necessity%2C%26quot%3B%20Salovaara%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he'd%20seen%20more%20of%20these%20US-focused%20startups%20in%20the%20past%20three%20years%20in%20Southeast%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225cba1264-76fb-426a-a579-946d29be1cab%5C%22%3ESoutheast%20Asia%20is%20growing%2C%20but%20it%20doesn't%20have%20the%20US's%20firepower%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESoutheast%20Asia%2C%20a%20group%20of%2011%20countries%20east%20of%20the%20Indian%20subcontinent%20and%20south%20of%20China%2C%20has%20seen%20skyrocketing%20economic%20growth%20over%20the%20past%20decade.%20Since%202015%2C%20the%20region's%20GDP%20has%20climbed%20more%20than%2062%25%20to%20%244.12%20trillion%2C%20boosted%20by%20a%20growing%20middle%20and%20upper%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%202015%20and%202021%2C%20the%20number%20of%20venture%20capital%20deals%20within%20the%20region%20more%20than%20tripled%20to%201%2C800%2C%20PitchBook%20data%20shows.%20Activity%20peaked%20in%202021%20%E2%80%94%20a%20similar%20pattern%20to%20startup%20funding%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FXQFut%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22asia%20vc%20deal%20count%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22435%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20region's%20growth%2C%20more%20Southeast%20Asia%20startups%20are%20choosing%20to%20focus%20on%20building%20products%20for%20the%20US%2C%20not%20for%20those%20around%20them.%20Founders%20and%20business%20experts%20note%20that%20the%20American%20market%20is%20more%20concentrated%2C%20more%20mature%2C%20and%20less%20price%20sensitive%2C%20all%20of%20which%20make%20it%20an%20attractive%20playing%20ground%20for%20new%20entrants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20the%20US%20is%20leading%20in%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20the%20major%20driver%20of%20today's%20global%20tech%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20in%20an%20AI-first%20world%20where%20currently%20the%20US%20is%20at%20the%20epicenter%20of%20driving%20groundbreaking%20advancements%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shailendra%20Singh%2C%20a%20managing%20director%20with%20Peak%20XV%2C%20the%20VC%20firm%20previously%20known%20as%20Sequoia%20Capital%20India%20%26amp%3B%20Southeast%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Bis%20why%20we%20put%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20focus%20and%20effort%20on%20building%20global%20go-to-market%20operating%20teams%20in%20the%20US.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20American%20businesses%20are%20happy%20to%20have%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSEA%20startups%20are%20often%20positioned%20to%20offer%20high-quality%2C%20cost-competitive%20solutions%20that%20can%20undercut%20US-based%20alternatives%2C%20making%20them%20appealing%20to%20American%20businesses%20in%20need%20of%20cost-effective%20innovation%2C%26quot%3B%20Antler's%20Salovaara%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20the%20model%20isn't%20unique%20to%20Southeast%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENataliya%20Wright%2C%20an%20entrepreneurship%20professor%20at%20Columbia%20Business%20School%2C%20researched%20startups%20founded%20from%202000%20to%202015%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpapers.ssrn.com%2Fsol3%2Fpapers.cfm%3Fabstract_id%3D5078041%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20forthcoming%20paper%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20scaling.%20She%20found%20that%20software%20startups%20from%20small%20countries%20in%20Europe%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20typically%20focused%20on%20the%20US%20from%20the%20get-go.%20Southeast%20Asian%20countries%20such%20as%20Thailand%20and%20Vietnam%2C%20however%2C%20are%20considered%20midsize%20markets%2C%20with%20populations%20in%20the%20tens%20of%20millions.%20Startups%20from%20midsize%20markets%20tended%20to%20start%20with%20a%20local%20focus%2C%20assuming%20there%20would%20be%20enough%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20US%20orientation%2C%26quot%3B%20Wright%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20%26quot%3Bwould%20suggest%20a%20departure%20from%20that%20model.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e0a17994-836e-4871-b295-33bf6c5cbb67%5C%22%3E11%20unique%20markets%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWorking%20only%20within%20the%20region%20is%20tough.%20Southeast%20Asia%20is%20home%20to%20a%20huge%20diversity%20of%20languages%2C%20business%20practices%2C%20and%20household%20incomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20spending%20five%20times%20more%20because%20you're%20entering%20five%20different%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20Khemlani%2C%20the%20JigsawStack%20founder%2C%20said%20about%20working%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20and%20tech%20hubs%20like%20San%20Francisco%20allow%20startups%20to%20find%20an%20abundance%20of%20customers%20in%20one%20place%2C%20or%20at%20least%20in%20one%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20have%20the%20resources%20to%20do%20two%20streams%20of%20marketing%2C%26quot%3B%20Khemlani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Yoeven%20Khemlani%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683483fa6ffb6822ec6177ce%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKhemlani%20founded%20JigsawStack%20in%202024.%3Cp%3EYoeven%20Khemlani%2FAntler%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20some%20American%20customers%20is%20good%20for%20fundraising%2C%20too%2C%20said%20Wright%2C%20the%20Columbia%20Business%20School%20professor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20because%20of%20a%20bias%20called%20%26quot%3Bforeign%20discounting%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20VCs%20based%20in%20startup%20hubs%20such%20as%20Silicon%20Valley%20overlook%20or%20undervalue%20startups%20founded%20elsewhere%2C%20Wright%20said.%20When%20foreign%20startups%20show%20they%20have%20US%20customers%2C%20it%20helps%20cancel%20out%20that%20bias%20and%20could%20give%20them%20a%20leg%20up%20in%20future%20fundraising%20rounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVCs%20say%20founders%20from%20the%20region%20have%20advantages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESingh%2C%20the%20Peak%20XV%20managing%20director%2C%20said%20Indian%20and%20Southeast%20Asian%20startups%20often%20have%20an%20underdog%20mindset.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20feel%20a%20startup%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%20is%20more%20polished%20and%20has%20better%20access%20to%20capital%20and%20talent%2C%20so%20they%20want%20to%20overcompensate%20by%20working%20harder%2C%20learning%20faster%2C%20and%20often%20they're%20understated%20and%20very%20hungry%20for%20success%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227de43a8b-8a9e-4db1-9429-f760d68693c9%5C%22%3EHotbed%20for%20innovation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERealfast%20is%20a%20Singaporean%20Peak%20XV-backed%20startup%20that%20builds%20AI%20agents%20for%20IT%20systems.%20Its%20cofounder%2C%20Sidu%20Ponnappa%2C%20has%20found%20that%20the%20US%20is%20the%20deepest%20market%20for%20its%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20from%20deal%20velocity%20to%20deal%20size%20operates%20at%20a%20completely%20different%20level%20in%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20Ponnappa%20said.%20%26quot%3BCan%20you%20do%20the%20same%20thing%20for%20other%20markets%3F%20Yes%2C%20but%20it's%20always%20lower%20margin.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Patsnap's%20founder%2C%20Jeffrey%20Tiong%2C%20and%20Guan%20Dian.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68348349c6ad288d1481e47b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22788%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPatsnap's%20founder%2C%20Jeffrey%20Tiong%2C%20and%20Guan%20Dian.%3Cp%3EPatSnap%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGuan%20Dian%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20Asia%20Pacific%20operations%20of%20Patsnap%2C%20a%20software%20maker%20for%20research%20and%20development%20projects%20that's%20backed%20by%20Vertex%20Ventures%2C%20said%20the%20company's%20founders%20always%20thought%20the%20US%20would%20be%20a%20priority%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20startup%20has%20customers%20in%2050%20countries%2C%20more%20than%20half%20of%20its%205%2C000%20customers%20are%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20company%20refined%20its%20branding%20to%20emphasize%20AI-powered%20features%20for%20industries%20such%20as%20biotech%20and%20advanced%20manufacturing%2C%20which%20dominate%20US%20patent%20filings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECost%20consciousness%20among%20Southeast%20Asian%20customers%20is%20another%20reason%20founders%20are%20reaching%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSoutheast%20Asia%20is%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20price%20sensitive%2C%20and%20we%20tend%20to%20get%20a%20bit%20more%20into%20negotiation%2C%26quot%3B%20Khemlani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECheaper%20labor%20means%20local%20customers%20try%20low-tech%20solutions%20or%20building%20themselves%20first%2C%20but%20that's%20starting%20to%20change%20as%20AI%20models%20get%20more%20complex%20and%20expensive%2C%20Khemlani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2288c78d8f-8934-4f65-852f-d52193474765%5C%22%3E'Should%20we%20move%20our%20headquarters%20to%20America%3F'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFounders%20don't%20want%20to%20fully%20decamp%20to%20the%20US%2C%20though%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20ease%20of%20doing%20business%20in%20places%20such%20as%20Singapore.%20For%20startups%20including%20Multiplier%2C%20an%20HR%20platform%20backed%20by%20Tiger%20Global%20and%20Peak%20XV%2C%20Singapore's%20strong%20geopolitical%20relations%20with%20virtually%20every%20country%20are%20a%20big%20advantage%20over%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20business%20with%20China%20and%20Taiwan%2C%20we%20do%20business%20with%20India%20and%20Pakistan%2C%20we%20do%20business%20with%20America%20and%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sagar%20Khatri%2C%20Multiplier's%20CEO%20and%20cofounder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20evaluated%20time%20and%20time%20again%3A%20Should%20we%20move%20our%20headquarters%20to%20America%3F%20And%20the%20answer%20has%20always%20been%20no%2C%26quot%3B%20Khatri%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sagar%20Khatri%20(center)%20with%20the%20cofounders%20of%20Multiplier.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683484656ffb6822ec6177d8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAmritpal%20Singh%2C%20Sagar%20Khatri%2C%20and%20Vamsi%20Krishna%20co-founded%20Multiplier.%3Cp%3EMultiplier%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20founders%20who%20spoke%20with%20BI%20also%20touted%20Singapore's%20tax%20policy%20%E2%80%94%20it%20doesn't%20tax%20capital%20gains%20%E2%80%94%20and%20government%20grants%20for%20tech%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20startups%20are%20splitting%20their%20people