20grandkids%20were%20too%20young%20to%20ride%2C%20but%20this%20past%20year%20seemed%20like%20the%20perfect%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20headed%20off%20to%20the%20gorgeous%20Alisal%20Ranch%20in%20Santa%20Ynez%20for%20a%20memorable%20girls-only%20trip%2C%20from%20Grandma%20to%20the%20six-year-old.%20It%20was%20clearly%20a%20property%20meant%20for%20family%20reunions%20and%20multigenerational%20vacations.%20The%20cabin%20we%20stayed%20in%20had%20a%20clever%20Murphy%20bunk%20bed%2C%20couch%20bed%2C%20and%20spacious%20bedroom%20for%20Grandma%20to%20rest%20comfortably.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20slower%20pace%20of%20trip%20that%20appealed%20to%20both%20young%20and%20old.%20Sitting%20on%20the%20porch%20watching%20horses%20meandering%20around%20while%20the%20sunsets%20will%20always%20remain%20a%20highlight%2C%20as%20will%20the%20friendly%20goats%20in%20the%20barn%20the%20kids%20went%20back%20day%20after%20day%20to%20pet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEating%20each%20meal%20together%20and%20just%20hanging%20out%20is%20basically%20what%20any%20grandparent%20really%20wants%2C%20and%20we%20had%20that%20in%20spades.%20The%20trip%20culminated%20in%20a%20wonderful%20morning%20horse%20ride%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bcowboy%20breakfast%26quot%3B%20(the%20youngest%20and%20I%20went%20in%20a%20wagon%20instead).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20all-inclusive%20nature%20of%20the%20property%20made%20it%20a%20super%20easy%20no-fuss%20planning%20process%20and%20everyone%20got%20to%20do%20what%20they%20wanted%2C%20whether%20it%20was%20just%20running%20around%20the%20expansive%20lawn%2C%20making%20crafts%20in%20the%20kids'%20art%20room%2C%20or%20playing%20ping-pong%20and%20roasting%20s'mores%20with%20Grandma.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20like%20me%20and%20have%20been%20sitting%20around%20wondering%20when%20to%20make%20a%20special%20trip%20with%20the%20grandparents%20happen%2C%20the%20answer%20is%20now.%20None%20of%20us%20are%20getting%20any%20younger%2C%20and%20it's%20such%20a%20precious%20window%20when%20everyone%20i