g%20the%20school%20with%20organisations%20like%20Universal%20General%20Insurance%20Company%2C%20which%20contributed%20Rs%209%20lakh%20to%20kickstart%20construction.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20Jamnabai%20Narsee%20School%20in%20Mumbai%20stepped%20in%20with%20funding%2C%20furniture%2C%20and%20by%20fostering%20beautiful%20exchange%20of%20ideas%20and%20values.%20Their%20students%20raised%20funds%20and%20visited%20Kelthan%20to%20understand%20rural%20education%20realities%20better%2C%20bridging%20a%20rarely%20crossed%20gap%20between%20urban%20and%20rural%20worlds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20like%20a%20barter%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gauri.%20%E2%80%9CCity%20students%20gave%20their%20time%20and%20resources%2C%20and%20in%20return%2C%20they%20received%20a%20grounded%2C%20eye-opening%20experience.%20It%20was%20about%20connecting%20the%20dots%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20worked.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPhase%202%20and%20beyond%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20work%2C%20however%2C%20isn%E2%80%99t%20over.%20unTAG%20has%20already%20completed%20the%20design%20for%20Phase%20two%2C%20which%20includes%20expanding%20the%20school%20to%20accommodate%20skill-based%20education%20for%20Classes%2011%20and%2012%2C%20in%20line%20with%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy.%20The%20team%20is%20now%20actively%20seeking%20donors%20and%20partners%20to%20help%20realise%20this%20next%20phase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20just%20about%20one%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tejesh.%20%E2%80%9COur%20goal%20is%20to%20create%20a%20replicable%20model%20%E2%80%94%20an%20ecosystem%20of%20rural%20schools%20that%20are%20sustainable%2C%20beautiful%2C%20and%20deeply%20rooted%20in%20their%20context.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Gauri%20and%20Tejesh%2C%20who%20both%20have%20rural%20connections%2C%20the%20project%20is%20personal.%20It%20is%20a%20fusion%20of%20passion%20and%20profession%2C%20a%20belief%20that%20good%20design%20should