n%20the%20roasted%20moong%20dal%20and%20pour%20enough%20water%20to%20cook%20everything%20gently%20(think%20soft%20and%20porridge-like).%20Let%20it%20simmer%20on%20medium%20heat%20for%20about%2020%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdd%20the%20fried%20veggies%20back%20into%20the%20pan%2C%20cover%2C%20and%20let%20everything%20bubble%20together%20for%20another%2010%20minutes.%20Your%20kitchen%20should%20smell%20amazing%20by%20now!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStir%20in%20a%20generous%20spoon%20of%20ghee%20and%20a%20handful%20of%20frozen%20peas.%20Add%20some%20slit%20green%20chilies%20if%20you%20like%20a%20bit%20of%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Beguni%2C%20slice%20brinjals%20into%20thin%20rounds%2C%20sprinkle%20with%20salt%20and%20turmeric%2C%20and%20let%20them%20sit%20for%20a%20few%20minutes.%20Heat%20oil%20in%20a%20pan%20and%20fry%20until%20crispy%20and%20golden%20brown%20on%20both%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EServe%20hot%20with%20a%20squeeze%20of%20lemon%20on%20top!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHappy%20monsoon!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Saumya%20Singh.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748673000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Finfosys-ad-banner-1746535509.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D441542%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indulge%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20monsoon%20flavours%20with%20delightful%20dishes%20like%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20immunity-boosting%20Karkidaka%20Kanji%2C%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20savoury%20Pundi%20Gatti%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%E2%80%99s%20crispy%20Egg%20Bonda%2C%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20aromatic%20Paa%20Saa%20soup%2C%20and%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20comforting%20Khichuri%20with%20brinjal%20fry.%20Perfect%20companions%20for%20rainy%20days!%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TBI%20Team%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F441542%2Ffive-tasty-monsoon-recipes-india-arunachal-kerala-karnataka%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%