y%20finally%20agreed%2C%20he%20trained%20Aasim%20not%20just%20to%20float%20or%20paddle%2C%20but%20to%20cross%20the%20river.%20It%20was%20a%20powerful%20moment%2C%20not%20just%20for%20Aasim%20but%20for%20everyone%20who%20watched%20him%20break%20through%20perceived%20limits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20river%20has%20seen%20many%20such%20milestones.%20One%20of%20Saji%E2%80%99s%20young%20students%20even%20made%20it%20to%20the%20Asian%20Book%20of%20Records%20for%20completing%20the%20longest%20solo%20open%20sea%20swim%20by%20a%20child%20%E2%80%94%20a%20feat%20born%20not%20of%20ambition%20alone%2C%20but%20of%20the%20joyful%2C%20disciplined%20training%20nurtured%20here%20each%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%205%3A30%20AM%20every%20morning%2C%20a%20quiet%20hum%20of%20excitement%20fills%20the%20air%20as%20the%20community%20gathers.%20Children%2C%20parents%2C%20elders%20all%20assemble%20along%20the%20water%E2%80%99s%20edge.%20Saji%20begins%20with%20gentle%20stretches%20and%20simple%20exercises%2C%20weaving%20in%20warmth%20and%20joy%20with%20stories%20and%20playful%20games.%20He%20turns%20safety%20drills%20into%20moments%20of%20fun%2C%20asking%20children%20if%20they%20know%20how%20to%20find%20their%20way%20home%2C%20encouraging%20impromptu%20performances%2C%20filling%20the%20air%20with%20laughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20sun%20rises%2C%20it%20casts%20its%20glow%20on%20a%20riverbank%20filled%20with%20smiling%2C%20spirited%20faces%2C%20ready%20to%20greet%20the%20water.%20When%20asked%20what%20keeps%20people%20coming%20back%2C%20Saji%20simply%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20go%20to%20places%20where%20they%20find%20happiness.%20Then%20swimming%20just%20becomes%20an%20added%20benefit.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Leila%20Badyari%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20%3Cem%3EAll%20pictures%20courtesy%20Valassery%20Swimming%20Club%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748595328000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Finfosys-ad-