%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fhailey-bieber-rhode-deal-with-elf-beauty_n_68383601e4b0e2e0f9a1b134%2Famp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20This%20Delhi-Based%20Company%20Saved%204.5%20Million%20Milk%20Packets%20From%20Ending%20Up%20in%20Landfills%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20decades%2C%20plastic%20has%20been%20both%20a%20marvel%20and%20a%20menace.%20Introduced%20to%20India%20in%20the%20mid-20th%20century%2C%20plastic%20quickly%20became%20a%20popular%20alternative%20to%20traditional%20materials%20due%20to%20its%20durability%2C%20flexibility%2C%20and%20low%20cost.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20it%20found%20its%20way%20into%20every%20aspect%20of%20life%20%E2%80%94%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F319630%2Fdesigner-turns-waste-material-into-eco-friendly-furniture-ek-kalakar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epackaging%20and%20furniture%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20infrastructure%20and%20fashion.%20But%20what%20once%20symbolised%20innovation%20has%20now%20become%20one%20of%20the%20planet%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20environmental%20threats.%20India%20alone%20generates%20over%203.4%20million%20tonnes%20of%20plastic%20waste%20annually%2C%20much%20of%20it%20ending%20up%20in%20landfills%20or%20choking%20rivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20not%20everyone%20sees%20plastic%20as%20the%20villain.%20%E2%80%9CPlastic%2C%20for%20me%2C%20is%20not%20a%20bad%20material%3B%20it%20is%20the%20poor%20disposal%20and%20not%20repurposing%20it%20that%20creates%20a%20huge%20issue%20for%20the%20planet%20and%20the%20natural%20resources%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Yuvraj%20Singh%20Ahuja%2C%20architect-turned-entrepreneur%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20%E2%80%98Sereno%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A0%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faarohan.infosys.org%2F%3Fcmpid%3Dsco_TheBetterIndia_EB_AarohanAwards25_foundation_banner_24042025_lq_Awareness_Rgn%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Finfosys-ad-banner-1746535509.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20out%20of%20Amritsar%20with%20a%20design%20office%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Yuvraj%20is%20making%20the%20best%20use%20of%20plastic%20trimmings%20and%20everyday%20plastics%20by%20converting%20them%20into%20100%25%20recyclable%20planters%20and%20furniture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20architect%20to%20entrepreneur%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYuvraj%E2%80%99s%20journey%20began%20in%20the%20family%20business.%20His%20father%20had%20established%20Frontier%20Polymers%20Pvt.%20Ltd.%20in%201990%2C%20manufacturing%20rotomoulded%20products%20like%20water%20tanks%20and%20household%20plastic%20items.%20As%20the%20only%20son%2C%20Yuvraj%20joined%20the%20business%20soon%20after%20graduating%20in%20architecture%20in%201999.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20business%2C%20I%20was%20trying%20to%20find%20a%20niche%20that%20appealed%20to%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2050-year-old%20says.%20That%20quest%20led%20him%20to%20introduce%20a%20road%20safety%20line%20%E2%80%94%20cones%20and%20barriers%20that%20are%20now%20a%20staple%20on%20highways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-28T175517.808-1748435141.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Yuvraj-%20the%20founder%20of%20Sereno%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-28T175517.808-1748435141.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-28T175517.808-1748435141-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-28T175517.808-1748435141-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-28T175517.808-1748435141-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-28T175517.808-1748435141-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-440437%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EYuvraj%20started%20Sereno%20with%20his%20mother%E2%80%99s%20idea%20of%20making%20pots%20and%20planters.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Yuvraj%E2%80%99s%20design%20instincts%20nudged%20him%20in%20another%20direction.%20The%20turning%20point%20came%20when%20his%20mother%20brought%20home%20a%20few%20cheap%20plastic%20pots.%20%E2%80%9CI%20thought%2C%20how%20can%20we%20create%20a%20better%20version%20in%20terms%20of%20design%20and%20durability%3F%E2%80%9D%20This%20question%20sparked%20the%20birth%20of%20Sereno%20in%202013%2C%20initially%20focusing%20on%20high-quality%2C%20beautifully%20designed%20planters%20and%20seats%20made%20from%20virgin%20plastic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20same%20year%2C%20Sereno%20won%20the%20CIA%20Design%20Excellence%20Award%2C%20a%20prestigious%20recognition%20by%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Interior%20Designers%20and%20the%20Gov